rgs. So my first step is to make that call.\n\nSo the first action is to invoke mcp with those parameters.\n\nLet me check the instructions again: \"Every mcp call must have exactly this shape: a tool string and an args string. Do not include action, server, or connect. Do not pass args as an object.\"\n\nSo in the mcp call, args is a JSON string. So for the first call, args is \"{}\", which is a string.\n\nSo in the tool call JSON, arguments should have \"tool\": \"aar_wait_for_opportunity\", \"args\": \"{}\".\n\nYes.\n\nSo the first step is to execute that mcp call.","contentIndex":0,"partial":{"api":"openai-completions","content":[{"thinking":"","thinkingSignature":"reasoning","type":"thinking"},{"arguments":{"args":"{}","tool":"aar_wait_for_opportunity"},"id":"call_0f05542e20cf40809e7c85","name":"mcp","type":"toolCall"}],"model":"qwen/qwen3-next-80b-a3b-thinking","provider":"openrouter","responseId":"gen-1781909886-T9TsgkiJMbM0UUH4txUM","responseModel":"qwen/qwen3-next-80b-a3b-thinking-2509","role":"assistant","stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781909885847,"usage":{"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"cost":{"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"input":0,"output":0,"total":0},"input":2406,"output":578,"totalTokens":2984}},"type":"thinking_end"},"message":{"api":"openai-completions","content":[{"thinking":"","thinkingSignature":"reasoning","type":"thinking"},{"arguments":{"args":"{}","tool":"aar_wait_for_opportunity"},"id":"call_0f05542e20cf40809e7c85","name":"mcp","type":"toolCall"}],"model":"qwen/qwen3-next-80b-a3b-thinking","provider":"openrouter","responseId":"gen-1781909886-T9TsgkiJMbM0UUH4txUM","responseModel":"qwen/qwen3-next-80b-a3b-thinking-2509","role":"assistant","stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781909885847,"usage":{"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"cost":{"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"input":0,"output":0,"total":0},"input":2406,"output":578,"totalTokens":2984}},"type":"message_update"}
